title: Oyen Digital MiniPro RAID V3 USB-C External Dual Bay Drive Enclosure
features: Interface: USB-C (Compatible with USB 3.1 and Thunderbolt 3). It is not compatible with Thunderbolt 2 or earlier.
Configurable for JBOD, RAID 0, RAID 1, & BIG modes. No software required.
Supports two 2.5-inch SATA drives (HDD or SSD) up to 15mm height
description: The MiniPro RAID V3 is a dual-drive storage enclosure offering the latest Type-C connection for compatibility with all USB and Thunderbolt 3. Built entirely from aluminum, the MiniPro RAID V3 utilizes the highest quality construction for power users who need dependable storage. The MiniPro RAID V3 can operate as two independent drives (default) or can be configured as a hardware RAID system. The MiniPro RAID V3 is compatible with SATA 2.5" drives (HDD/SSD) and provides for an easy installation process.
